chapters.title: Prologue:  Snow
chapters.info: Lady Birgitte Trahelion, p. 26 (14)—Captain-General of the Queen's Guards under Elayne, and her Warder. She is allegedly from Kandor. She is actually Birgitte, a Hero of Legend, bound to the Horn of Valere until Moghedien ripped her away. See Birgitte.
